                                    text="&lt;p>If you have employer-provided insurance coverage or have purchased private insurance on your own, you may qualify for assistance with your out-of-pocket expenses. Learn more by selecting your medicine below:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <text_346176090
