savings-support/qulipta-complete-savings-program&quot;>QULIPTA&lt;sup>TM&lt;/sup> (atogepant) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.allergantechalliance.com/Resources/Patient-Savings&quot;>Restasis® (cyclosporine) ophthalmic emulsion&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rinvoq.com/resources/save-on-rinvoq-costs&quot;>RINVOQ™ (upadacitinib)&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.allergansavingscard.com/savella&quot;>Savella® (milnacipran HCl) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.skyrizi.com/skyrizi-complete/save-on-skyrizi-costs&quot;>SKYRIZI™ (risankizumab-rzaa)&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.synthroid.com/support/before-breakfast-club?signup=true&quot;>Synthroid® (levothyroxine sodium) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ubrelvy.com/udemand#u-save&quot;>Ubrelvy® (ubrogepant) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>VENCLEXTA™ (venetoclax tablets)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;For information about patient assistance for VENCLEXTA please&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.genentech-access.com/patient/brands/venclexta.html&quot;>click&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;or call 1-888-249-4918.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.viberzi.com/savings-program&quot;>Viberzi® (eluxadoline) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.viibryd.com/savings-program&quot;>Viibryd® (vilazodone HCl) tablets&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.allergansavingscard.com/vraylar&quot;>Vraylar® (cariprazine) capsules&lt;/a>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Vyalev™ (foscarbidopa/foslevodopa)&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Please call 1-866-489-2538 (1-866-4VYALEV) for information.&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
